    <item>
      <title>本田预计利润将稳定增长，并表示将进行更多股票回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/honda-expects-firm-profit-growth-flags-more-share-repurchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司预计，由于混合动力汽车和两轮车的强劲需求，本财年利润将稳步增长，并表示将回购更多股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/honda-expects-firm-profit-growth-flags-more-share-repurchases</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果在审查后即将完成首次国际货币基金组织贷款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-10/congo-nears-first-ever-imf-loan-program-completion-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于华盛顿特区的国际货币基金组织周三给予积极评价后，刚果民主共和国历史上首次向完成国际货币基金组织贷款计划又迈进了一步。彭博新闻社的翁迪罗·奥甘加 (Ondiro Oganga) 在中东和非洲地平线节目中与 Joumanna Bercetche 进行讨论。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-10/congo-nears-first-ever-imf-loan-program-completion-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:13:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济衰退以解除封锁以来最强劲的增长结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国从浅度衰退中强劲反弹，让迄今为止一直在努力兑现经济增长承诺的首相里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)松了口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/uk-says-recession-ended-with-stronger-than-expected-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗下调中国股市评级，上调印度股市盈利前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/citi-cuts-china-stocks-on-fundamentals-to-neutral-raises-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团的策略师将高速发展的中国股市评级下调至中性，认为尽管基本面疲软，但近期的反弹还是出现了。该团队将新兴市场竞争对手印度的评级上调至“增持”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/citi-cuts-china-stocks-on-fundamentals-to-neutral-raises-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 05:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市相对于香港股市的溢价迅速消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/chinese-stocks-discount-over-hong-kong-peers-may-be-fading-fast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通过中国交易通在香港购买的股票可能获得股息税豁免，中国股票相对于香港上市的溢价已经缩水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/chinese-stocks-discount-over-hong-kong-peers-may-be-fading-fast</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 04:29:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股息和房地产推动香港股市创九个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对可能取消部分股息税以及促进中国房地产购买的新举措的乐观情绪，香港基准股指跃升至九个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 01:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对美国降息的乐观情绪重燃，油价延续两天涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业数据支持美联储今年降息，提振了包括原油在内的风险资产，油价连续第三天上涨，创一周高位。]]></description>
